<p>Wow: Megan McKenna, 27, put on a sultry display as she posed braless in a cream crochet crop top for an Instagram post on Sunday</p>

<p>Resting her hands on her jeans, Megan looked every inch the star as she stared down the lens of the camera for the social media post. </p>

<p>The X Factor: Celebrity winner wore her shoulder-length locks in a bouncy blow dry and accessorised with gold hoop earrings. </p>

