<p>Finishing her look, the beauty added a statement gold watch and a single bangle on her wrist. </p>

<p>Captioning the snap, she wrote: 'Megan show me your best game face.' </p>

<p>Last month it was reported that Megan is 'smitten' with her new businessman beau Josh after he won her heart over during a series of fancy dinner dates. </p>

<p>Captioning the snap for the Instagram post, she wrote: '"Megan show me your best game face"'</p>

